var book = {
	"name": "1 John",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>What was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542A\"></sup>from the beginning, what we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542B\"></sup>heard, what we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542C\"></sup>seen with our eyes, what we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542D\"></sup>have looked at and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542E\"></sup>touched with our hands, concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30542F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30542F\"></sup>Word of Life—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543G\"></sup>the life was manifested, and we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543H\"></sup>seen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543I\"></sup>testify and proclaim to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543J\"></sup>the eternal life, which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543K\"></sup>with the Father and was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30543L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30543L\"></sup>manifested to us—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>what we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30544M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30544M\"></sup>seen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30544N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30544N\"></sup>heard we proclaim to you also, so that you too may have fellowship with us; and indeed our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30544O\"></sup>fellowship is with the Father, and with His Son Jesus Christ.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30545P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30545P\"></sup>These things we write, so that our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30545Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30545Q\"></sup>joy may be made complete.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30546R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30546R\"></sup>This is the message we have heard from Him and announce to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30546S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30546S\"></sup>God is Light, and in Him there is no darkness at all.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30547T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30547T\"></sup>If we say that we have fellowship with Him and <i>yet</i> walk in the darkness, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30547U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30547U\"></sup>lie and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30547V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30547V\"></sup>do not practice the truth;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30548W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30548W\"></sup>walk in the Light as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30548X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30548X\"></sup>He Himself is in the Light, we have fellowship with one another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30548Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30548Y\"></sup>the blood of Jesus His Son cleanses us from all sin.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30549Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30549Z\"></sup>If we say that we have no sin, we are deceiving ourselves and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30549AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30549AA\"></sup>truth is not in us.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30550AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30550AB\"></sup>If we confess our sins, He is faithful and righteous to forgive us our sins and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30550AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30550AC\"></sup>to cleanse us from all unrighteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30551AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30551AD\"></sup>If we say that we have not sinned, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30551AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30551AE\"></sup>make Him a liar and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30551AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30551AF\"></sup>His word is not in us."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30552A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30552A\"></sup>My little children, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30552B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30552B\"></sup>writing these things to you so that you may not sin. And if anyone sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30552C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30552C\"></sup>we have an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30552D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30552D\"></sup>Advocate with the Father, Jesus Christ the righteous;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and He Himself is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30553E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30553E\"></sup>the propitiation for our sins; and not for ours only, but also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30553F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30553F\"></sup>for <i>those of</i> the whole world.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30554G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30554G\"></sup>By this we know that we have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30554H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30554H\"></sup>know Him, if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30554I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30554I\"></sup>keep His commandments.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The one who says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30555J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30555J\"></sup>I have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30555K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30555K\"></sup>know Him,” and does not keep His commandments, is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30555L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30555L\"></sup>liar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30555M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30555M\"></sup>the truth is not in him;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30556N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30556N\"></sup>keeps His word, in him the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30556O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30556O\"></sup>love of God has truly been perfected. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30556P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30556P\"></sup>By this we know that we are in Him:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>the one who says he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30557Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30557Q\"></sup>abides in Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30557R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30557R\"></sup>ought himself to walk in the same manner as He walked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30558S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30558S\"></sup>Beloved, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30558T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30558T\"></sup>not writing a new commandment to you, but an old commandment which you have had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30558U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30558U\"></sup>from the beginning; the old commandment is the word which you have heard.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On the other hand, I am writing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30559V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30559V\"></sup>a new commandment to you, which is true in Him and in you, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30559W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30559W\"></sup>the darkness is passing away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30559X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30559X\"></sup>the true Light is already shining.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The one who says he is in the Light and <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30560Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30560Y\"></sup>hates his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30560Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30560Z\"></sup>brother is in the darkness until now.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30561AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30561AA\"></sup>The one who loves his brother abides in the Light and there is no cause for stumbling in him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30562AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30562AB\"></sup>hates his brother is in the darkness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30562AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30562AC\"></sup>walks in the darkness, and does not know where he is going because the darkness has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30562AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30562AD\"></sup>blinded his eyes.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I am writing to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30563AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30563AE\"></sup>little children, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30563AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30563AF\"></sup>your sins have been forgiven you for His name’s sake.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am writing to you, fathers, because you know Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30564AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30564AG\"></sup>who has been from the beginning. I am writing to you, young men, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30564AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30564AH\"></sup>you have overcome <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30564AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30564AI\"></sup>the evil one. I have written to you, children, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30564AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30564AJ\"></sup>you know the Father.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have written to you, fathers, because you know Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30565AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30565AK\"></sup>who has been from the beginning. I have written to you, young men, because you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30565AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30565AL\"></sup>strong, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30565AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30565AM\"></sup>word of God abides in you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30565AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30565AN\"></sup>you have overcome the evil one.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do not love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30566AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30566AO\"></sup>the world nor the things in the world. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30566AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30566AP\"></sup>If anyone loves the world, the love of the Father is not in him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For all that is in the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30567AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30567AQ\"></sup>the lust of the flesh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30567AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30567AR\"></sup>the lust of the eyes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30567AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30567AS\"></sup>the boastful pride of life, is not from the Father, but is from the world.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30568AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30568AT\"></sup>The world is passing away, and <i>also</i> its lusts; but the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30568AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30568AU\"></sup>does the will of God lives forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30569AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30569AV\"></sup>it is the last hour; and just as you heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30569AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30569AW\"></sup>antichrist is coming, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30569AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30569AX\"></sup>even now many antichrists have appeared; from this we know that it is the last hour.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30570AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30570AY\"></sup>They went out from us, but they were not <i>really</i> of us; for if they had been of us, they would have remained with us; but <i>they went out</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30570AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30570AZ\"></sup>so that it would be shown that they all are not of us.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But you have an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30571BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30571BA\"></sup>anointing from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30571BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30571BB\"></sup>the Holy One, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30571BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30571BC\"></sup>you all know.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I have not written to you because you do not know the truth, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30572BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30572BD\"></sup>because you do know it, and because no lie is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30572BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30572BE\"></sup>of the truth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Who is the liar but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30573BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30573BF\"></sup>the one who denies that Jesus is the Christ? This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30573BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30573BG\"></sup>the antichrist, the one who denies the Father and the Son.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30574BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30574BH\"></sup>Whoever denies the Son does not have the Father; the one who confesses the Son has the Father also.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>As for you, let that abide in you which you heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30575BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30575BI\"></sup>from the beginning. If what you heard from the beginning abides in you, you also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30575BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30575BJ\"></sup>will abide in the Son and in the Father.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30576BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30576BK\"></sup>This is the promise which He Himself made to us: eternal life.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>These things I have written to you concerning those who are trying to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30577BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30577BL\"></sup>deceive you.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>As for you, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30578BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30578BM\"></sup>anointing which you received from Him abides in you, and you have no need for anyone to teach you; but as His anointing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30578BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30578BN\"></sup>teaches you about all things, and is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30578BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30578BO\"></sup>true and is not a lie, and just as it has taught you, you abide in Him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30579BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30579BP\"></sup>little children, abide in Him, so that when He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30579BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30579BQ\"></sup>appears, we may have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30579BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30579BR\"></sup>confidence and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30579BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30579BS\"></sup>not shrink away from Him in shame at His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30579BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30579BT\"></sup>coming.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>If you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30580BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30580BU\"></sup>He is righteous, you know that everyone also who practices righteousness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30580BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30580BV\"></sup>is born of Him."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>See <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30581A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30581A\"></sup>how great a love the Father has bestowed on us, that we would be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30581B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30581B\"></sup>children of God; and <i>such</i> we are. For this reason the world does not know us, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30581C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30581C\"></sup>it did not know Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582D\"></sup>Beloved, now we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582E\"></sup>children of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582F\"></sup>it has not appeared as yet what we will be. We know that when He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582G\"></sup>appears, we will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582H\"></sup>like Him, because we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30582I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30582I\"></sup>see Him just as He is.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And everyone who has this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30583J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30583J\"></sup>hope <i>fixed</i> on Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30583K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30583K\"></sup>purifies himself, just as He is pure.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Everyone who practices sin also practices lawlessness; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30584L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30584L\"></sup>sin is lawlessness.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You know that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30585M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30585M\"></sup>appeared in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30585N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30585N\"></sup>take away sins; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30585O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30585O\"></sup>in Him there is no sin.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>No one who abides in Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30586P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30586P\"></sup>sins; no one who sins has seen Him or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30586Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30586Q\"></sup>knows Him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30587R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30587R\"></sup>Little children, make sure no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30587S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30587S\"></sup>deceives you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30587T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30587T\"></sup>the one who practices righteousness is righteous, just as He is righteous;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the one who practices sin is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30588U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30588U\"></sup>of the devil; for the devil has sinned from the beginning. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30588V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30588V\"></sup>The Son of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30588W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30588W\"></sup>appeared for this purpose, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30588X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30588X\"></sup>to destroy the works of the devil.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30589Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30589Y\"></sup>born of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30589Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30589Z\"></sup>practices sin, because His seed abides in him; and he cannot sin, because he is born of God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>By this the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30590AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30590AA\"></sup>children of God and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30590AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30590AB\"></sup>children of the devil are obvious: anyone who does not practice righteousness is not of God, nor the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30590AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30590AC\"></sup>does not love his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30590AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30590AD\"></sup>brother.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30591AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30591AE\"></sup>For this is the message <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30591AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30591AF\"></sup>which you have heard from the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30591AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30591AG\"></sup>that we should love one another;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>not as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30592AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30592AH\"></sup>Cain, <i>who</i> was of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30592AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30592AI\"></sup>the evil one and slew his brother. And for what reason did he slay him? Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30592AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30592AJ\"></sup>his deeds were evil, and his brother’s were righteous.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not be surprised, brethren, if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30593AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30593AK\"></sup>the world hates you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We know that we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30594AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30594AL\"></sup>passed out of death into life, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30594AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30594AM\"></sup>because we love the brethren. He who does not love abides in death.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30595AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30595AN\"></sup>hates his brother is a murderer; and you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30595AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30595AO\"></sup>no murderer has eternal life abiding in him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>We know love by this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30596AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30596AP\"></sup>He laid down His life for us; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30596AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30596AQ\"></sup>we ought to lay down our lives for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30596AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30596AR\"></sup>brethren.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30597AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30597AS\"></sup>whoever has the world’s goods, and sees his brother in need and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30597AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30597AT\"></sup>closes his heart against him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30597AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30597AU\"></sup>how does the love of God abide in him?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30598AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30598AV\"></sup>Little children, let us not love with word or with tongue, but in deed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30598AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30598AW\"></sup>truth.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We will know by this that we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30599AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30599AX\"></sup>of the truth, and will assure our heart before Him",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>in whatever our heart condemns us; for God is greater than our heart and knows all things.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30601AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30601AY\"></sup>Beloved, if our heart does not condemn us, we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30601AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30601AZ\"></sup>confidence before God;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30602BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30602BA\"></sup>whatever we ask we receive from Him, because we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30602BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30602BB\"></sup>keep His commandments and do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30602BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30602BC\"></sup>the things that are pleasing in His sight.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>This is His commandment, that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30603BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30603BD\"></sup>believe in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30603BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30603BE\"></sup>the name of His Son Jesus Christ, and love one another, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30603BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30603BF\"></sup>He commanded us.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30604BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30604BG\"></sup>keeps His commandments <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30604BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30604BH\"></sup>abides in Him, and He in him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30604BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30604BI\"></sup>We know by this that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30604BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30604BJ\"></sup>He abides in us, by the Spirit whom He has given us."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30605A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30605A\"></sup>Beloved, do not believe every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30605B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30605B\"></sup>spirit, but test the spirits to see whether they are from God, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30605C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30605C\"></sup>many false prophets have gone out into the world.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>By this you know the Spirit of God: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30606D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30606D\"></sup>every spirit that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30606E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30606E\"></sup>confesses that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30606F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30606F\"></sup>Jesus Christ has come in the flesh is from God;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and every spirit that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30607G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30607G\"></sup>does not confess Jesus is not from God; this is the <i>spirit</i> of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30607H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30607H\"></sup>antichrist, of which you have heard that it is coming, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30607I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30607I\"></sup>now it is already in the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You are from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30608J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30608J\"></sup>little children, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30608K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30608K\"></sup>have overcome them; because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30608L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30608L\"></sup>greater is He who is in you than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30608M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30608M\"></sup>he who is in the world.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30609N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30609N\"></sup>They are from the world; therefore they speak <i>as</i> from the world, and the world listens to them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30610O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30610O\"></sup>We are from God; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30610P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30610P\"></sup>he who knows God listens to us; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30610Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30610Q\"></sup>he who is not from God does not listen to us. By this we know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30610R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30610R\"></sup>the spirit of truth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30610S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30610S\"></sup>the spirit of error.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30611T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30611T\"></sup>Beloved, let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30611U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30611U\"></sup>love one another, for love is from God; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30611V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30611V\"></sup>everyone who loves is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30611W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30611W\"></sup>born of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30611X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30611X\"></sup>knows God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The one who does not love does not know God, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30612Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30612Y\"></sup>God is love.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By this the love of God was manifested <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30613Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30613Z\"></sup>in us, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30613AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30613AA\"></sup>God has sent His only begotten Son into the world so that we might live through Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In this is love, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30614AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30614AB\"></sup>not that we loved God, but that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30614AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30614AC\"></sup>He loved us and sent His Son <i>to be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30614AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30614AD\"></sup>the propitiation for our sins.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30615AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30615AE\"></sup>Beloved, if God so loved us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30615AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30615AF\"></sup>we also ought to love one another.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30616AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30616AG\"></sup>No one has seen God at any time; if we love one another, God abides in us, and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30616AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30616AH\"></sup>love is perfected in us.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30617AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30617AI\"></sup>By this we know that we abide in Him and He in us, because He has given us of His Spirit.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We have seen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30618AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30618AJ\"></sup>testify that the Father has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30618AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30618AK\"></sup>sent the Son <i>to be</i> the Savior of the world.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30619AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30619AL\"></sup>Whoever confesses that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30619AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30619AM\"></sup>Jesus is the Son of God, God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30619AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30619AN\"></sup>abides in him, and he in God.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30620AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30620AO\"></sup>We have come to know and have believed the love which God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30620AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30620AP\"></sup>for us. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30620AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30620AQ\"></sup>God is love, and the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30620AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30620AR\"></sup>abides in love abides in God, and God abides in him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>By this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30621AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30621AS\"></sup>love is perfected with us, so that we may have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30621AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30621AT\"></sup>confidence in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30621AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30621AU\"></sup>the day of judgment; because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30621AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30621AV\"></sup>as He is, so also are we in this world.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is no fear in love; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30622AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30622AW\"></sup>perfect love casts out fear, because fear involves punishment, and the one who fears is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30622AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30622AX\"></sup>perfected in love.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30623AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30623AY\"></sup>We love, because He first loved us.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30624AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30624AZ\"></sup>If someone says, “I love God,” and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30624BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30624BA\"></sup>hates his brother, he is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30624BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30624BB\"></sup>liar; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30624BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30624BC\"></sup>the one who does not love his brother whom he has seen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30624BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30624BD\"></sup>cannot love God whom he has not seen.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30625BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30625BE\"></sup>this commandment we have from Him, that the one who loves God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30625BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30625BF\"></sup>should love his brother also."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30626A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30626A\"></sup>Whoever believes that Jesus is the Christ is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30626B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30626B\"></sup>born of God, and whoever loves the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30626C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30626C\"></sup>loves the <i>child</i> born of Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30627D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30627D\"></sup>By this we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30627E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30627E\"></sup>we love the children of God, when we love God and observe His commandments.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30628F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30628F\"></sup>this is the love of God, that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30628G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30628G\"></sup>keep His commandments; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30628H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30628H\"></sup>His commandments are not burdensome.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For whatever is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30629I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30629I\"></sup>born of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30629J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30629J\"></sup>overcomes the world; and this is the victory that has overcome the world—our faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who is the one who overcomes the world, but he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30630K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30630K\"></sup>believes that Jesus is the Son of God?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is the One who came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30631L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30631L\"></sup>by water and blood, Jesus Christ; not with the water only, but with the water and with the blood. It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30631M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30631M\"></sup>the Spirit who testifies, because the Spirit is the truth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30632N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30632N\"></sup>three that testify:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the Spirit and the water and the blood; and the three are in agreement.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30634O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30634O\"></sup>If we receive the testimony of men, the testimony of God is greater; for the testimony of God is this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30634P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30634P\"></sup>He has testified concerning His Son.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The one who believes in the Son of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30635Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30635Q\"></sup>has the testimony in himself; the one who does not believe God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30635R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30635R\"></sup>made Him a liar, because he has not believed in the testimony that God has given concerning His Son.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the testimony is this, that God has given us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30636S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30636S\"></sup>eternal life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30636T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30636T\"></sup>this life is in His Son.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30637U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30637U\"></sup>He who has the Son has the life; he who does not have the Son of God does not have the life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30638V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30638V\"></sup>These things I have written to you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30638W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30638W\"></sup>believe in the name of the Son of God, so that you may know that you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30638X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30638X\"></sup>eternal life.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30639Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30639Y\"></sup>the confidence which we have before Him, that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30639Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30639Z\"></sup>if we ask anything according to His will, He hears us.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And if we know that He hears us <i>in</i> whatever we ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30640AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30640AA\"></sup>we know that we have the requests which we have asked from Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If anyone sees his brother committing a sin not <i>leading</i> to death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30641AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30641AB\"></sup>he shall ask and <i>God</i> will for him give life to those who commit sin not <i>leading</i> to death. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30641AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30641AC\"></sup>There is a sin <i>leading</i> to death; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30641AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30641AD\"></sup>I do not say that he should make request for this.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30642AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30642AE\"></sup>All unrighteousness is sin, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30642AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30642AF\"></sup>there is a sin not <i>leading</i> to death.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30643AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30643AG\"></sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30643AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30643AH\"></sup>no one who is born of God sins; but He who was born of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30643AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30643AI\"></sup>keeps him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30643AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30643AJ\"></sup>the evil one does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30643AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30643AK\"></sup>touch him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30644AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30644AL\"></sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30644AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30644AM\"></sup>we are of God, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30644AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30644AN\"></sup>the whole world lies in <i>the power of</i> the evil one.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AO\"></sup>we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AP\"></sup>the Son of God has come, and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AQ\"></sup>given us understanding so that we may know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AR\"></sup>Him who is true; and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AS\"></sup>are in Him who is true, in His Son Jesus Christ. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AT\"></sup>This is the true God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30645AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30645AU\"></sup>eternal life.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30646AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30646AV\"></sup>Little children, guard yourselves from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30646AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30646AW\"></sup>idols."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;